data.description: Situated on over 2 acres, this well maintained, split level, 4 bedroom home, with an amazing backyard setting is waiting for you! 2 full baths plus 2 half baths with a family room and living room creates a nice spacious feel when you enter the home. Located on a nice corner lot with rural views and a huge yard that has an invisible fence to allow your pets plenty of space to run. A nicely landscaped backyard boasts a shed, pool, hot tub, covered deck, and TV area ready to host gatherings. Attached two car garage ready for all your storage needs. Come check this home out today! The inside pics will be up by 11/3/2023.
